      "csl:pageColumn": "3,1",
      "rdf:value": "<L>423<pc>3,1<k1>akz<k2>akz<e>1\r\n<s>akz</s> ¦ (perhaps a kind of old <ab>Desid.</ab> of √ <hom>1.</hom> <s>aS</s>) <ab>cl.</ab> 1. 5. <s>akzati</s>, <s>akzRoti</s> (<ls>Pāṇ. iii, 1, 75</ls>; <ab>fut.</ab> <s>akzizyati</s> or <s>akzyati</s>, <ls>L.</ls>; <ab>aor.</ab> <s>AkzIt</s>, 3. <ab>du.</ab> <s>AkzizwAm</s> or <s>AzwAm</s>, <ls>L.</ls>; <ab>perf.</ab> <s>Anakza</s> [<ls>Pāṇ. vii, 4, 60</ls> <ab>Comm.</ab>], but <ab>Ā.</ab> <ab>p.</ab> [with the Vedic weak stem <s>Akz</s> <ab>cf.</ab> <ab>perf.</ab> <s>AS-uH</s> 3. <ab>pl.</ab> &c. <ab>fr.</ab> √ <hom>1.</hom> <s>aS</s>] <s>AkzARa/</s>),\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to reach, <ls>RV. x, 22, 11</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to pass through, penetrate, pervade, embrace, <ls>L.</ls>;\r\n<div n=\"to\"/>to accumulate (to form the cube?), <ls>L.</ls> :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Caus.</ab> <s>akzayati</s>, <s>Acikzat</s>, to cause to pervade, <ls>L.</ls> :\r\n<div n=\"vp\"/><ab>Desid.</ab> <s>acikzizati</s> or <s>acikzati</s>, <ls>L.</ls><info whitneyroots=\"akz1,1;akz2,1\"/><info verb=\"genuineroot\" cp=\"1,5\"/><listinfo n=\"sup\"/>\r\n<LEND>"
    },
    {
      "@id": "https://sanskrit-lexicon.github.io/csl-standards/id/case/mw-pwg-pwk%3Aakz#record-pwg",
      "@type": "csl:SourceRecord",
      "dct:source": "Boehtlingk-Roth PWG",
      "csl:dictionary": "pwg",
      "csl:recordNumber": "165",
      "csl:lineNumber": 1321,
      "csl:pageColumn": "1-0013",
      "rdf:value": "<L>165<pc>1-0013<k1>akz<k2>akz\n{#akz#}¦, {#a/kzati#} und {#akzRo/ti#}\n<ls>P. 3,1,75.</ls>\n<ls>VOP. 8,74.</ls> {#Anakza#}\n<ls>P. 7,4,60</ls>, <is>Vārtt</is>. 1. {#akzitA#} und {#azwA; akzizyati#} und {#akzyati; AkzIt, AkzizwAm#} oder {#AzwAm#}\n<ls>VOP. 8,75.</ls> {#akzitvA#} oder {#azwvA; azwa#} .\n<div n=\"1\"> 1) {%erreichen, treffen%}: {#ma\\kzU tA ta^ indra dA\\nApna^sa AkzA\\Re#} (<ab>d. i.</ab> {#AnAkzARe) SU^ra vajrivaH . yadDa\\ SuzRa^sya da\\mBayo^ jA\\taM viSva^M sa\\yAva^BiH ..#}\n<ls>ṚV. 10,22,11.</ls>\n<div n=\"1\">— 2) {%durchdringen, erfüllen%} ({#vyAptO#})\n<ls>DHĀTUP.</ls> <ls>NAIGH. 2,18.</ls> ({#A\\kzA\\RaH#}).\n<div n=\"1\">— 3) {%anhäufen%} ({#saMGAte#})\n<ls>DHĀTUP.</ls> — <ab>Caus.</ab> {#akzayati, Acikzat#} . — <ab>Desid.</ab> {#acikzizati#} und {#acikzati#} .\n<div n=\"v\">— <ab>Vgl.</ab> {#aS#} .\n<div n=\"p\">— {#nis#} {%zerstreuen, aus einander jagen%}: {#i\\mami^ndra varDaya kza\\triya^M ma i\\maM vi\\SAme^kavf\\zaM kf^Ru\\ tvam . nira\\mitrA^~ akzRuhyasya\\ sarvA\\~stAnra^nDayAsmA ahamu\\ttarezu^ ..#}\n<ls>AV. 4,22,1.</ls>\n<div n=\"p\">— {#sam#} {%durchgehen, durchwandern%}: {#tvaM devi brahmalokaM samakzase#} (Med.)\n<ls>R. 2,52,80.</ls>\n<LEND>"
    },
